    "## 2. Target Distribution - Who Are We trying to find? \n",
    "\n",
    "In a real hospital screening programme, class balance tells us something important: how often does heart disease actually occur in this population? A model that predicts \"Absence\" every time would score ~55% accuracy while being completely useless clinically. We need to know the baseline before declaring any accuracy impressive."
   ]
